	.sfpr, and correct case where either only savef* or restf* is
	needed.

	Long branch stubs, multiple stub sections.
	* elf64-ppc.h (ppc64_elf_setup_section_lists): Declare.
	(ppc64_elf_next_input_section): Declare.
